
meta-rno-g
============

This layer contains customizations on top of meta-ampliphy for the RNO-G experiment

It is meant to be used on top of a phytec-headless-image for the AM62X SOM

To use, you probably want to set up the environment as specified on the on the phytec website, then add this layer.


Cosmin Deaconu <cozzyd@kicp.uchicago.edu>
